50
00:02:55,074 --> 00:02:59,111
         He was kind of
      a bad dude, you know.

51
00:02:59,179 --> 00:03:01,613
         Terry McBride:
   I'm not going to say I had

52
00:03:01,681 --> 00:03:03,448
    a problem with authority,

53
00:03:03,516 --> 00:03:05,717
       I think they had a
    problem with me because I

54
