65
00:03:29,409 --> 00:03:32,844
     Richard Rubio: We were
    goofing off all the time,

66
00:03:32,912 --> 00:03:38,083
   always getting in trouble,
    and we had a lot of fun.

67
00:03:38,134 --> 00:03:40,852
     Terry McBride: I never
    knew that a bunch of guys

68
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:46,158
     could get as tied as we
 did in a short period of time.

69
00:03:48,261 --> 00:03:51,029
     Larry Lilley: One day,
    we were part way through

70
00:03:51,164 --> 00:03:54,433
        training and Don
    Peterson is screwing up.

71
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:57,669
       He's joking around
   and having a good time and

72
00:03:57,737 --> 00:04:00,472
      the drill instructor
    is not happy about that.

73
00:04:00,540 --> 00:04:03,642
         So he yells for
    Peterson, "Get up here!"

74
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:06,011
     And the drill sergeant
      says, "On your back,

75
00:04:06,079 --> 00:04:08,313
        hands and legs in
       the air and scream.

76
00:04:08,381 --> 00:04:11,583
     'I'm a bug' til we are
     done with our workout."

77
