     "I'm a bug, I'm a bug!"

79
00:04:17,857 --> 00:04:21,293
         And when PT was
        over he was Bug.

80
00:04:21,361 --> 00:04:26,698
     From then on he wasn't
    Don Peterson he was Bug!

81
