    President Johnson: I have
   come here tonight to report

93
00:05:09,142 --> 00:05:12,444
   to you that this is a time
   of testing for our nation.

94
00:05:12,512 --> 00:05:14,546
      Ron Nessen: The North
   Vietnamese and the Vietcong

95
00:05:14,614 --> 00:05:17,049
      are obviously trying
   to stay away from any major

96
00:05:17,116 --> 00:05:20,118
       head on fights with
     American combat units,

97
00:05:20,186 --> 00:05:22,187
     but the communists are
   continuing their offensive

98
00:05:22,255 --> 00:05:25,957
      in the form of terror
     and guerrilla strikes.

99
00:05:26,025 --> 00:05:28,860
       President Johnson:
    I wish I could report to

100
00:05:28,895 --> 00:05:30,696
          you that the
    conflict is almost over.

101
