        These things were
   jolting all over the place

161
00:09:37,777 --> 00:09:40,445
   and swaying back and forth.

162
00:09:40,513 --> 00:09:42,614
       I look back now and
    I can laugh about it but

163
00:09:42,682 --> 00:09:47,185
        at the time, man,
    it was pretty miserable.

164
00:09:48,854 --> 00:09:50,989
    Steve Hopper: Then there
    were days that the water

165
00:09:51,057 --> 00:09:52,924
       was just beautiful.

166
00:09:52,992 --> 00:09:56,161
     Just as smooth as glass
    and you'd enjoy your days

167
00:09:56,228 --> 00:10:00,832
      out on the top deck.

168
00:10:03,502 --> 00:10:06,571
     There's a lot of things
     going through your mind

169
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:08,940
       before you actually
       enter a combat zone

170
00:10:09,008 --> 00:10:10,842
      as to whether or not,
   what your capabilities are.

171
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:13,078
        Regardless of the
      training you've had,

172
00:10:13,145 --> 00:10:16,681
          everybody has
       a soul about them.

173
