   tracers off in the distance
 coming down from a helicopter.

186
00:11:15,007 --> 00:11:17,308
          And all of a
       sudden you realize,

187
00:11:17,376 --> 00:11:22,247
        Wow, there's some
      stuff going on here.

188
00:11:24,450 --> 00:11:27,485
      Bill Reynolds: We had
    to gather all of our gear

189
00:11:27,553 --> 00:11:30,955
   and get ready to disembark
