190
00:11:31,023 --> 00:11:32,624
         a smaller boat,

191
00:11:32,692 --> 00:11:36,628
      a landing craft that
    was to take us to shore.

192
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:43,868
            You know,
      it was kind of scary,

193
00:11:43,886 --> 00:11:46,671
         we didn't know
         what to expect.

194
00:11:49,542 --> 00:11:53,011
    John Bradfield: The gate
  came down and we came ashore,

195
00:11:53,079 --> 00:11:56,981
      and we're all looking
