197
00:12:00,753 --> 00:12:07,092
     What we found out was,
  that it was a reception area.

198
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:09,694
         Bill Reynolds:
   They immediately loaded us

199
00:12:09,762 --> 00:12:13,131
  on deuce-and-a-halfs and all
  of a sudden we find ourselves

200
00:12:13,199 --> 00:12:17,869
  busting down this dirt road,
     dust flying everywhere.

201
00:12:21,574 --> 00:12:24,642
  John Sclimenti: We're driving
    through and we could see

202
00:12:24,710 --> 00:12:28,513
      these little houses,
   people were working and the

