00:12:28,581 --> 00:12:33,118
     animals that they were
 using to plough the fields with

204
00:12:33,185 --> 00:12:38,089
      and the bicycles and
   the little motor scooters.

205
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:44,295
          Gary Maibach:
    The sites and the sounds

206
00:12:44,363 --> 00:12:51,136
   and the smells of a totally
