211
00:13:11,090 --> 00:13:12,624
          Gary Maibach:
       And there we were.

212
00:13:12,691 --> 00:13:14,726
            No tents,
      no cots, no nothing.

213
00:13:14,794 --> 00:13:18,196
    Welcome to Vietnam, guys!

214
00:13:20,249 --> 00:13:22,967
       Bill Reynolds: They
    had us digging trenches,

215
00:13:23,035 --> 00:13:25,870
        filling sandbags,
  we were instantly working our

216
00:13:25,921 --> 00:13:29,007
          tails off to
      build our base camp.

217
00:13:31,327 --> 00:13:33,278
          John Hoskins:
       Hello mom and dad.

218
00:13:33,329 --> 00:13:36,180
    Here I am safe and sound
     at the scenic Bear Cat,

219
00:13:36,282 --> 00:13:41,786
    Republic of Vietnam, the
    armpit of southeast Asia.

220
