    Right now I'm sitting in
   my tent eating two brownies

221
00:13:45,090 --> 00:13:47,625
       which were sent by
   Lieutenant Benedick's wife.

222
00:13:47,693 --> 00:13:49,894
    Now I know you don't know
   who in the hell Lieutenant

223
